Team: get person

get_person.Rd

Team: get person

get_person(x)

Arguments

x

one element of css-class="li-employee-item" (as retrieved by kwb.site::get_team_url())

Value

tibble with information of one person

Examples

#' @examples
 if (FALSE) {
 rs <- kwb.site::rs_connect()
 team_html <- kwb.site::get_team_html(rs = rs)
 team <- team_html %>%
 rvest::html_nodes("li.employee-item")
 kwb.site::get_person(team[1])
 }
